  <span id="freeText439492302026163942" style="display:none"> The day I had been awaiting had finally arrived I could sink myself into book four of The Keeper Series, Sanctuary. With baited anticipation I began to read knowing within minutes that this book was not what I had foreseen. Each character in this series had grown stronger as they set out to save earth from the struggle of good versus evil and yet each still held a special place in me. As each scene played before me it was like watching a sexy paranormal Die Hard movie! I giggled to myself as I waited to hear one phrase Yippee Ki Yay *&amp;%#$@ @*^%#^ only I knew it would not be there. I have been with this series from the very first book The Keeper Awakening and it has become stronger, bolder, and darker as time passes and each book as come to life. I can't tell you how it all will end up as that is Mr. Ramos's job I will tell you that this series has been one I look forward to reading with each new installment. Give it a try what have you got to lose the first one The Keeper Awakening is free.</span>
